      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver who values both performance and mechanical reliability. Meticulously maintained and presenting a refined aesthetic, the automobile has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards. With a well-preserved interior and a robust powertrain, this unit offers a superior driving experience and exceptional value within its class.",
