    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six power plant. This unit boasts a crisp throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and remains robust thanks to a proactive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. While showing honest patina consistent with its age, the chassis remains rigid with refreshed bushings and a well-damped suspension geometry. A driver-focused example that prioritizes longitudinal and lateral performance over concours perfection.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
