    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride in ownership, offering a balanced blend of performance and comfort. The exterior features a sleek metallic finish that still carries a brilliant shine, though it shows a few honest signs of the road like minor stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin remains a refined sanctuary with premium leather upholstery that has been carefully conditioned; there is only slight wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, while the rear seats appear nearly untouched. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been strictly maintained according to the factory schedule, with a comprehensive folder of service records included for the new owner. Recent updates include a fresh oil service and a new set of brake pads within the last 2,000 miles. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. All onboard technology, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, is fully operational. This is a dependable, well-cared-for machine ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
